{
  "id": "adv_main_02_03_01",
  "title": "東京編1章11話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_main-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0.03333333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――TRINITYAiLEが入所して",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――A few days have passed",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "しばらく経ったある日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After TRINITYAiLE transferred to Hoshimi Productions",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_01-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "なんだか久しぶりですね。こうして五人揃って\n{user}さんと会うのは",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It feels like it’s been forever since the five of us got together\nto visit you here‚ {user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.333333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ここのところ、仕事が忙しかったからな\n俺も、サニーピースのみんなも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’ve all been busy with work lately.\nBoth myself and all of you at Sunny Peace.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.277123898150876,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_01-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "最近はグループ活動の他に\nソロの仕事も増えてきましたからね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ in addition to group activities‚\nwe’ve all gotten more solo work as well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.110457231484208,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_01-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "今日は雫ちゃんがラジオに生出演するのよね？\nそれから千紗ちゃんは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Shizuku-chan‚ you have a live appearance on the radio today‚ right?\nAnd Chisa-chan has…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.47712389815087,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_01-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "午後からグラビア撮影です\n私一人なんて不安だけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "An afternoon gravure photoshoot.\nI’m a little worried about being alone‚ though…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.17712389815087,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_01-stm001.m4a",
      "text": "白石さんのグラビアはいつも評判いいですよ\n兵藤さんのラジオは……賛否両論ですけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But Shiraishi-san's gravure photoshoots are always very well-received!\nThough Hyodo-san’s radio appearances… get mixed reviews.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.481123799,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_01-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "私もさっきまで雑誌のインタビューを受けていたわ\n東京に進出してからみんな忙しくなったわよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And I just finished a magazine interview.\nEveryone’s gotten so busy since we moved to Tokyo.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.889370016091654,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_01-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "仕事が増えるのはいいこと……\n人気が出てきた証拠……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Having more work is a good thing.\nIt’s proof of our popularity.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.92270334942499,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "……うん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Yeah.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.02270334942499,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_01-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "忙しいのはいいことだよね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Being busy is a good thing!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.15603668275833,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_01-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "私はテレビの食レポの収録があるんだけど……\nなんだか私だけ仕事がバラエティ寄りじゃないかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m going to be a food reporter on a TV show.\nIs it just me‚ or am I the only one doing variety show work?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.622703349425,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_01-stm002.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さん\nバラエティもアイドルの大事なお仕事ですよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haruko-san.\nVariety shows are an important part of an idol’s job!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.48937001609166,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_01-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "それで、{user}さん\n今日は大事な話があるって聞いたんですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ {user}-san‚\nyou said you had something important to tell us today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.42270334942499,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そのことなんだが……\nみんな、心して聞いて欲しい……実は……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ about that…\nI want you all to listen carefully. You see…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.622703349425,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "……サニーピースの新曲を出すことが決まったぞ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sunny Peace is going to release a new song!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.82270334942498,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_happy-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 88.00562857372918
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_01-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "ええっ、本当ですか！\nやったー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ehhh? Really?!\nYay!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.93896190706252,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_01-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "新曲……楽しみ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A new song… Can’t wait.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.84832690937677,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_01-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "へえ、どんな曲になるのかしら\n誰が作詞・作曲するか、もう決まってるんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ooh‚ I wonder what kind of song it’s going to be.\nHave you already decided on a lyricist and composer?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.41499357604344,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "そのことで俺から提案があるんだ……今度の新曲は\nみんなで作詞と作曲にチャレンジしてみないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I actually have a proposal. For your newest song‚\nwould all of you like to try your hand at songwriting?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.3483269093768,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_01-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "私達が作詞と作曲の両方を？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You want us to write the lyrics and compose the song?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.21499357604345,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "前はみんなで作詞をしたけど、今度は作曲にも挑戦して\nよりみんなの個性をアピールしたいんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You wrote the lyrics together last time‚ but I’d like you to try composing as well.\nI think that would help promote your uniqueness.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.41626352055228,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_01-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "私、やってみたいです！\n新曲をみんなと一緒に作りたい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’d love to try it!\nI want to make a new song with everyone!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.94959685388568,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_01-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "でも、作曲なんて出来るかな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But can we really compose?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.91626352055236,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_01-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫よ\nみんなで力を合わせれば、きっといいものが出来るわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’ll be fine.\nIf we all work together‚ I’m sure we can create something good.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.35943808936443,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_01-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "私達で……最強のアイドルソングを作る……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let’s work together… to create the perfect idol song!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.55943808936445,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_01-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "そうと決まれば、さっそく作戦会議をするわよ\nさとみさん、事務所の会議室は空いてますか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now that’s decided‚ let’s have a brainstorming session.\nSatomi-san‚ is the conference room available?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.59277137501425,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_01-stm003.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　今日は会議室を使う予定はありませんから\n自由に使っていただいて構いません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes! There aren’t any meetings scheduled for today.\nFeel free to use it as you wish.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.95943804168104,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_01-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあみんな\n会議室に移動して新曲の打ち合わせをしよう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay‚ ladies‚\nlet’s move to the conference room and discuss our new song.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.6261047083478,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_01/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "後のことは、橋本さんにお願いしてもいいかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hashimoto-san‚ may I ask you to oversee the rest?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.19277137501447,
      "sfxList": []
